ption\n- node disk read I/O consumption \n- node disk write I/O consumption \n- node disk space consumption\n\nAnomaly Cluster Description:\nHere is the RCA analysis result in plain English:\n\n```\n{\n  "Cluster 1": {\n    "Key Findings": [\n      "High CPU usage by adservice2.ts:8088, causing frequent garbage collection",\n      "Increased container file system writes on node-5.frontend-1",\n      "Slow request duration for shippingservice-1.source.shippingservice.jaeger-collector"\n    ],\n    "Related Entities": [\n      "adservice2.ts:8088",\n      "node-5.frontend-1",\n      "shippingservice-1.source.shippingservice.jaeger-collector"\n    ],\n    "Root Cause": "High CPU usage by adservice2.ts:8088, causing cascading effects on other services"\n  },\n  "Cluster 2": {\n    "Key Findings": [\n      "Continued high CPU usage by adservice2.ts:8088",\n      "Increased container file system writes on node-5.frontend-1",\n      "Slow request duration for shippingservice-1.source.shippingservice.jaeger-collector"\n    ],\n    "Related Entities": [\n      "adservice2.ts:8088",\n      "node-5.frontend-1",\n      "shippingservice-1.source.shippingservice.jaeger-collector"\n    ],\n    "Root Cause": "Continued high CPU usage by adservice2.ts:8088, causing sustained performance issues"\n  },\n  "Cluster 3": {\n    "Key Findings": [\n      "Brief spike in CPU usage by adservice2.ts:8088",\n      "Log anomaly on cartservice-1 due to socket exception"\n    ],\n    "Related Entities": [\n      "adservice2.ts:8088",\n      "cartservice-1"\n    ],\n    "Root Cause": "Brief CPU spike by adservice2.ts:8088, potentially causing log anomaly on cartservice-1"\n  },\n  "Cluster 4": {\n    "Key Findings": [\n      "Single instance of high CPU usage by adservice2.ts:8088",\n      "Log anomaly on frontend-1->checkoutservice-0 due to frequency issue"\n    ],\n    "Related Entities": [\n      "adservice2.ts:8088",\n      "frontend-1->checkoutservice-0"\n    ],\n    "Root Cause": "Single ins